 Serpent ways of love
 Kdo vydrží trochu angličtiny? A kdo vydrží číst až do konce? Menší poémek o
 lásce.

 SERPENT WAYS OF LOVE

 Saw her one day going out
 with her friends, all laughing loud
 noticing not sun above
 I completely fell in love

 Stalking a bit I just had to see
 this beauty who had bewitched me
 not eating nor sleeping for few days
 I filled with her my fantasy
 you know - love does have serpent ways

 As she walked late from a music club
 I decided to make her stop
 saying her only word or two
 telling her just my: "I love you
 listen to me, just don't run
 you extraordinary one
 I love you, I want to share with thee
 my eternal life, please come with me."
 But I didn't say that at all...

 As we stood silent face to face
 my heart had told me to embrace
 to hug, to kiss this girl I want
 but from my lips slipped only "Don't-"
 "What?&quo t; smiled she, sparkling in her eyes
 in my voice sounded apologize
 "oh - don't you want me to drive you home?
 The night is falling and you're alone."
 She replied: "Thanks, that's very nice.
 Also I think my bus had gone."
 "So, come on board!" - she obeyed -
 "We girls must help each other, hey?"

 Driving a highway, noticing
 that she is looking for some thing
 touching the pockets of her jeans
 I heared her: "Where I have my keys?"
 And after few minutes of search of some,
 I noticed that my turn had come
 "You can go by, you're welcome, please!
 Come with me to my little home."
 "OK," she said, "and where is it?"
 "Just down there in the Oxford street.
 I'll make a dinner and something to drink
 you can sleep there and tomorrow I bring
 you back to your place, satisfied?"
 "You're such a good girl," she replied.
 "but there's no need - I'll go on foot,
 I'm living near in neighbourhood"

 Then she was there and once undressed
 my flat was filled with happiness
 and when she to the next room came
 she stared a while and then she claimed:
 "Oh, what a big-screened TV there!"
 "Do, watch a movie for time I'll cook."
 "Thanks, OK, let me have a look-"
 said she and search the tubes for Crime.
 Behind her back I spent my time
 looking on her nice golden hair
 pretending hunt for a cooking book.

 I had just put the food on the table
 when she claimed: "There! If I'm not able
 to loose somewhere my stupid head!
 Those keys were all time in my bag."
 I felt my cheeks are going red.
 "But will you rather stay instead
 going now. Also you must check
 this gorgeous meal I made for you."
 "OK," she smiled, "now sit down, too."

 I watched her eating, watched her lips
 her lovable small fingertips
 her skin so smooth and hair so bright
 her sapphire eyes with inner light
 her thin long legs and like a bow
 ner neck that I would kiss right now
 deep down inside, if there's a chance
 I wished to take her innocence...

 With my hand reaching slow her knee
 as I was drowning in dreams of love
 she laid the fork and looked at me -
 and I realised she knows enough.
 She looked at me and it was clear -
 from my world she will disappear.

 "I have to go," she whispered then
 and I felt that I loose again.
 "Forgive me! I just thought you're shaking -
 aren't you cold? I'll make you tea.
 There are few hours left till morning,
 just watch the movie and stay here."

 Oh goodness - what bollocks I'm telling!
 "Please, don't leave me now, please don't!"
 and what a voice - my throat was swelling
 and suddenly I simply won't
 to let her go, to be alone.
 Wanting to feel the pain is gone,
 to never again feel depressed,
 to suffer no more loneliness...

 then, under press of circumstance
 it completely got out my hands
 so when she shaked her head and turned
 I reached her neck with deadly grasp
 and as my head kept freeze and burn
 I only heared her howling gasp...

 Now I'm so shocked that I just stare
 on the girls body, on my bare
 hands I killed her with - no way back
 I strangled her like maniac...

 No, no, no way! This isn't true!
 Oh my god, look what you have done!
 Look at her, what she did to you?!
 Although I didn't want to be
 killing again, it's like a spree
 my downward spiral, flipping off
 comming back to me, round and round
 always when I feel loosing love...
 and now it happened, again
 I'm definitely insane...

 But on the other hand
 now, when it's done, what's point of regret?
 The beauty is killed and forever dead.
 Now in the four or five future days
 will she be mine, my lover so real.
 Until she's here, there's no need to kill.

 That is what goes my love's serpent ways...
  serpentways [Žena]24  _V_Y_M_A_Z_A_T

